  "response": "Love typically lasts longer than hate. While hate can be intense and consuming, love has the potential to be more enduring, transformative, and deeper. Healthy, genuine love can:\n\n1. Evolve and adapt over time\n2. Build strong emotional connections\n3. Promote understanding and empathy\n4. Heal and support relationships\n5. Sustain through challenges\n\nHate, on the other hand, tends to be more destructive and often burns out or consumes the person feeling it. Love has more potential for long-term positive impact.",
